And I recently came across @lotus_herbals new #probrite Range of Skincare- India’s 1st Probiotic Skincare Range!

It’s a blend of active Sakura flower extracts and Lactcocus Ferment Lysate to boost skin’s good bacteria and give it an unmatched radiance. 
Just Follow Three Steps to get Healthy Skin!!
Step1-Lotus Probrite Illuminating Radiance Cleansing Foam washes away traces of dust
Step2-Lotus Probrite Illuminating Radiance Day Creme improve the complexion and strengthen skin
Step3- Lotus Probrite Illuminating Radiance Night Creme gives clear and glowing skin

Head to their page and get your hands on their Probrite Range!!

latestIgtvVideos.title: Pampering Session @toniandguylucknow
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
What’s better than a New Hairstyle?
Thank you @toniandguylucknow for this Transformation I’m in love with my Hair.

Recently visited @toniandguylucknow for some grooming session and had a delightful experience.
I have opted for Hairstyling session, got Beach Curls and AROMA Manicure+Pedicure service which was so relaxing.

Well trained and talented staff does know what hairstyle would suit you and I’m extremely happy with the service. Perfect salon to spend your weekend by pampering yourself @toniandguylucknow 

And yes they are taking all safety measures during this crucial time.
